com.kedzie.vbox

Class BundleBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kedzie.vbox.BundleBuilder

  • public class BundleBuilder
extends Object
    Builder pattern for Bundle. Also contains functionality for wrapping VirtualBox remote proxies in Parcels
